rows.label: qst711001_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, there. What do you
think of this state-of-the-art
Superbian flagship?

rows.label: qst711001_msg0003
rows.name:
The only downside is that the modern
tech makes us mechanics cry...

rows.label: qst711001_msg0004
rows.name:
Every time I'm anchored in port, I'm
always so busy with repairs... Haven't
been home in such a long time.

rows.label: qst711001_msg0005
rows.name:
The longer you spend flying round
Alst, the more you start to yearn
for the taste of home.

rows.label: qst711001_msg0006
rows.name:
I tried to make a recipe my
mother used to make from memory,
but it didn't go too well...

rows.label: qst711001_msg0007
rows.name:
Hey, you wouldn't happen to
have someone who can cook
in your party, would you?

rows.label: qst711001_msg0008
rows.name:
If I tell you the recipe, do you
think you could cook up some food
from my hometown, Chilsain?

rows.label: qst711001_msg0009
rows.name:
Excellent! Looking forward to
some delicious home-cooked food!
Mmm, I can taste it already!
